{"tid":2072652,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"少於6萬人投票　未達發起跨工會聯合罷工門檻","createTime":"2020-06-20T17:29:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-20T17:47:08.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f2b963a172460bb2c69a497a624e50c743cd2b0b","tid":2072652,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T17:29:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1533231-20200621.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1533231-20200621.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=KvAiISINul4H2q03UsPduScuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=6434683a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1533231-20200621.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=e94ac43c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1533231-20200621.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n30個工會聯同學生組織發起公投，決定是否啟動罷工罷課，抗議港區國安法。在罷工公投方面，30個工會總投票人數為近9000人，少於6萬人投票的目標，當中只有6個工會達到罷工門檻，未能達到發起跨工會聯合罷工的門檻。<br />\n<br />\n在近9000票之中，有98%反對港區國安法，有約95%同意發起罷工。數名工會代表向投票人士鞠躬致謝。<br />\n<br />\n香港酒店工會主席徐考澧表示，這個投票結果是事前沒有預料過，同時亦沒有預料過在打壓下，有人站出來成為新會員參與公投，反映有一股新力量正在蘊釀。至於後續行動方面，徐考澧說，會與所有工會商議，現時未有明確行動。"},{"pid":"4fc42aea5dd25dca61583e8c947365470547191b","tid":2072652,"uid":13856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T17:35:34.000Z","msg":"一萬人都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77c2e72f1ee3198c96e555e48c82ab8763f86a9c","tid":2072652,"uid":335303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T17:42:27.000Z","msg":"唔好再俾藉口自己啦<br />\n<br />\n 諗下一步點做仲好"},{"pid":"161d663b994eefa9d01904233674906ae7b0f7da","tid":2072652,"uid":191399,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T17:47:08.000Z","msg":"要罷工就會罷 <br />\n好似之前幾次咁<br />\n唔洗公投<br />\n公投完全多餘"}]}